# ds4-agent launch defaults, in argv form.
#
# Activate by copying this file to either location (ds4-agent reads both, the
# per-user file winning; the command line still overrides everything):
#
#   <install dir>/default.cfg     shipped next to the ds4-agent binary
#   ~/.ds4/default.cfg            per-user overrides
#
# Syntax: one or more flags per line. '#' begins a comment. Quote values that
# contain spaces (e.g. -sys "You are a ..."). Relative model/--mtp paths and the
# metal shader sources resolve against the executable directory, so ds4-agent
# works from any directory (including off $PATH) with no --chdir.
#
# Disable this file for one run with --no-config; point at another file with
# --config FILE.

# --- Speculative decoding (DSpark) ---
# Helps most on greedy / code-style workloads; see the model notes before
# leaving it on for long thinking-mode sessions.
--dspark
--mtp gguf/DeepSeek-V4-Flash-DSpark-support.gguf

# --- Sampling ---
--temp 0.6
--top-p 0.95

# --- Context and generation budget ---
--ctx 196608
--tokens 12288

# --- Runtime ---
--threads 12
--prefill-chunk 4096
